## SYSTEM OVERVIEW

The Alchemy Signal System (AlchemyPerpBot) is a fully automated crypto perpetual futures trading system that detects Bollinger Band squeeze-to-expansion patterns on Bybit USDT perps, evaluates signals through a multi-gate pipeline with market context enrichment, sends alerts via Telegram, and executes trades via a separate execution engine. 5 of 6 planned agents are deployed and running.

**Owner:** Yuri (DomMazzetti1)
**Strategy:** SQ_SHORT — BB squeeze detection, short-biased, active in bear/sideways regimes
**Stack:** Next.js 14, Supabase (Postgres), Upstash Redis, Bybit V5 API, Anthropic Claude API, Telegram Bot API
**Status:** LIVE on Bybit mainnet since March 31, 2026

