## SIGNAL PIPELINE FLOW (Updated April 3)

```
Scanner (hourly cron)
  → Detect BB squeeze on 42 symbols
  → Tier: STRICT / RELAXED / DATA_ONLY
  → Burst rank by composite_score DESC
  → Portfolio Manager: max 3, no dupes, correlation filter
  → For each accepted candidate:
    → Gate A: Data quality (advisory)
    → Gate B: Regime + stop dist + volume + rr_tp1 >= 0.8
    → Signal Enrichment: attach funding/OI/spread/BTC context from data collector
    → Claude AI Review (Haiku): confidence + setup type
    → Risk Manager: position cap, daily loss, heat, burst dampener
    → Compute entry/stop/TP levels (1.0/2.0/3.5R)
    → Store decision with 7 enrichment columns
    → Telegram filter chain
    → If passes: Telegram → webhook to exec engine
  → Grade after 48h (dynamic ladder R from stored prices)
```

