## ENRICHMENT LAYER (NEW — April 3)

Three-stage pipeline: Data Collector → Derived Metrics → Signal Enrichment → Researcher

**Data Collector** (VPS, every 15 min): Per symbol — price, funding_rate, OI, spread, volume. Computes derived: OI delta 1h/4h, BTC beta, BTC correlation (Pearson), annualized funding, avg spread.

**Signal Enrichment** (Vercel, per signal): Attaches 7 columns to every decision: signal_funding_rate, signal_funding_interval, signal_oi_delta_1h_pct, signal_oi_delta_4h_pct, signal_spread_pct, signal_btc_correlation, signal_btc_beta.

**Researcher** (Vercel, daily/weekly): Pre-computes win rate breakdowns by OI direction, funding direction, BTC correlation. Sends computed analysis to Sonnet. Includes enrichment_insights in Telegram.

