## BACKTEST BLIND SPOTS (Discovered Live)

1. Burst correlation: all stop out together (portfolio manager now prevents)
2. Regime transition lag: 20 hours for EMA200 detection
3. Funding costs: BARD ate $61 in hourly funding
4. TP too far: Entries found direction but TP1 at 1.5R reversed (now 1.0R)
5. Ghost positions: handleSlHit race condition (now fixed)
6. Orphan positions: Reconciler only logged, didn't act (now auto-closes)

